examples.en: The room was saturated with smoke.
His shirt was saturated with sweat.
The market was saturated with the fruit.
Our clothes were saturated with the sudden heavy rain.
examples.ru: Вся наша одежда промокла из-за внезапно хлынувшего дождя.

examples.en: Our culture is saturated with television and advertising.
examples.ru: Наша культура насыщена телевидением и рекламой.

examples.en: The book is saturated with Hollywood.
Images of the war saturated the news.
examples.ru: Новости были насыщены фотографиями с войны.
